Patch Set 12:

oslo.config generator was wrapping lines at 70 characters. That was the reason for the absolute formatting to cause the extra line breaks in the conf files. The solution to have the right formatting in the conf files is to maintain a 70 character line limit while adding the help texts in absolute formatting mode mode.
Resubmitting with this approach.

Patch Set 13: Code-Review+1

I think this is a decent compromise until we figure out if there's a way to change oslo config generator work well with absolute formatting.

We could probably get pep8 to check for 70 character limit for config help text, too.
